{"tid":2055661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"解釋每次BNO平權或有進展，件澳門人在英國又出嚟踩","createTime":"2020-06-08T06:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T17:05:53.000Z","uid":231480,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ebe24680c95ff56802b9bbdbbcf16eeb0b9367ae","tid":2055661,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/bno-%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A-working-holiday-2-0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2Fbno-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25AC%258A-working-holiday-2-0%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=35e473d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2Fbno-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25AC%258A-working-holiday-2-0%2F&h=485c278f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/bno-%E5%B9%B3%E6%AC%8A-working-holiday-2-0/</a><br />\n<br />\n// &hellip;其實最理想的方法，當然是直接平權，賦與所有合資格 BNO 人士英國公民身份。但無論是約翰遜還是藍韜文的發言，都小心翼翼對此事絕口不提，僅提及工作或讀書，是提供他們取得英國公民身份的一個途徑（pathway / route）&hellip; //<br />\n<br />\n香港人爭取BNO又關你咩事，自己拎葡國護照喺英國住就唔想其他BNO港人有居英權<br />\n<br />\n利申唔係世柒"},{"pid":"8dbe94a4dcebf6c4d2eac78fc75b419b991e7131","tid":2055661,"uid":22839,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">早前我已撰文指，若給予 BNO 人士入境英國 12 個月，但工作或讀書要另外取得簽證的話，即使給予免簽入境 12 個月並可續期，仍然沒有實質作用，因為不少國家的人都可以免簽入境英國，找到工作或學校之後轉簽證，分別不大。</span><br />\n<br />\n見到呢段已經知佢唔撚識, 收皮啦"},{"pid":"01626e8daef64526a9e727bdfb55bd2d0df5e9f6","tid":2055661,"uid":231480,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8dbe94a4dcebf6c4d2eac78fc75b419b991e7131","tid":2055661,"uid":22839,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">早前我已撰文指，若給予 BNO 人士入境英國 12 個月，但工作或讀書要另外取得簽證的話，即使給予免簽入境 12 個月並可續期，仍然沒有實質作用，因為不少國家的人都可以免簽入境英國，找到工作或學校之後轉簽證，分別不大。</span><br />\n<br />\n見到呢段已經知佢唔撚識, 收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"其實最想香港人冇居英權係咪佢<br />\nBtw世柒有時好膠"},{"pid":"65fbb13dea2d69e084a12c23bb6e4544ea3e6fa2","tid":2055661,"uid":262480,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T06:50:15.000Z","msg":"佢都白撚癡<br />\n英國都要顧當地嘅人感受<br />\n試下水溫都好正常"},{"pid":"372d48fe79db380922974cf34ec7dc3ab0974fed","tid":2055661,"uid":9681,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"關條澳門狗撚事，點解佢成撚日寫bno？收咗錢定係有鋪癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad2a9dc08aa4bb519828570085585bb2054cc1d","tid":2055661,"uid":9681,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"372d48fe79db380922974cf34ec7dc3ab0974fed","tid":2055661,"uid":9681,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"關條澳門狗撚事，點解佢成撚日寫bno？收咗錢定係有鋪癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"平咗權嘅話佢係咪要自殺？定係煽動英國人搞種族歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb05ae27d02ab185805cc610829ca853a69dc1a","tid":2055661,"uid":18477,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"372d48fe79db380922974cf34ec7dc3ab0974fed","tid":2055661,"uid":9681,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"關條澳門狗撚事，點解佢成撚日寫bno？收咗錢定係有鋪癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"想show off佢自己個葡籍嘅優勢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98459434aa00a74f18b75edb44a0250d94d0dde5","tid":2055661,"uid":70013,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8bb05ae27d02ab185805cc610829ca853a69dc1a","tid":2055661,"uid":18477,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"372d48fe79db380922974cf34ec7dc3ab0974fed","tid":2055661,"uid":9681,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T